#summary jsCore Count property.
#labels Phase-Implementation

*syntax:*
{{{
object.Count ' [Number]
}}}

If you use an auto rename it includes a new auto value.

== Samples ==

{{{
<!--#include file="JSON_lastest.asp"-->
<%
Dim o
Set o = jsObject()

o(Null) = "ali"
Response.Write o.Count
o(Null) = 43
Response.Write o.Count

o.Flush
%>
}}}
